<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Sun on Compossible</title><link>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/tags/sun/</link><description>Recent content in Sun on Compossible</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-GB</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 01:08:27 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://compossible.asym-intel.info/tags/sun/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Moon</title><link>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2026/03/08/moon/</link><pubDate>Sun, 08 Mar 2026 15:31:03 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2026/03/08/moon/</guid><description>&lt;hr>
&lt;p>The Moon is the promise of the Sun&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Fear not, tomorrow will come&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Just look at its&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Astonished face&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Locked in place&lt;/p>
&lt;p>To think&lt;/p>
&lt;p>It cannot look away&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Not once&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Forgive us…&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Some things&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Are unspeakable&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Even in reflection&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>I bathed in moonbeams last night&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Showered in its fulgent light&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>We Are Dawn</title><link>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2025/09/11/we-are-dawn/</link><pubDate>Thu, 11 Sep 2025 18:55:48 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2025/09/11/we-are-dawn/</guid><description>&lt;p>Poem and AI song &amp;amp; video&lt;/p>
