&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C9cXDk0qxY0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;amp;utm_campaign=loading">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C9cXDk0qxY0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;amp;utm_campaign=loading">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C9cXDk0qxY0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;amp;utm_campaign=loading">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C9cXDk0qxY0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;amp;utm_campaign=loading">View this post on Instagram&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C9cXDk0qxY0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;amp;utm_campaign=loading">A post shared by Peter Pink-Howitt (@peterhowitt)&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>We Are Dawn&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Shy moon&lt;br>
Hiding with&lt;br>
Dwining stars&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://compossible.asym-intel.info/images/uploads/2025/09/shy-moon.webp" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;h2>&lt;/h2>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Slow sun&lt;br>
Sauntering o’er&lt;br>
Weald and tor&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://compossible.asym-intel.info/images/uploads/2025/09/sun.png" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Green land&lt;br>
Breathing loam&lt;br>
Seeding sky&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>